{
  "_comment": "Same hiring pipeline as ../hiring-pipeline.json, but modules are referenced by ID from modules.json. Demonstrates the external reference pattern AND multi-language strings.",
  "meta": {
    "title": {
      "en": "Hiring Pipeline (with module references)",
